{"id": "1233257479463505971", "channel_id": "1231906620980596757", "type": 0, "author_id": "848454386598412318", "author_name": "ruko9999", "author_bot": false, "content": "我是認為內文主題就是寫一個版本最多能獲得的銀芯有多少\n然後這些銀芯期望值能抽個4隻左右\n所以抽卡的時候要考慮自己的隊伍構成需不需要而已\n專注在325這點上有點怪", "timestamp": "2024-04-26T03:24:55.920000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1231906620980596757", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "七萬銀芯囤囤鼠教你如何以性價比最高的方式實現資源管理！", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1227516925479747584", "1174179680056791130", "1174180524034637854"]}
{"id": "1233257957706305656", "channel_id": "1231906620980596757", "type": 0, "author_id": "848454386598412318", "author_name": "ruko9999", "author_bot": false, "content": "這是屯屯鼠攻略 又不是什麼正論教學 對吧（X", "timestamp": "2024-04-26T03:26:49.942000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1231906620980596757", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "七萬銀芯囤囤鼠教你如何以性價比最高的方式實現資源管理！", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1227516925479747584", "1174179680056791130", "1174180524034637854"]}
{"id": "1233258033354772551", "channel_id": "1231906620980596757", "type": 0, "author_id": "392840163732226058", "author_name": "vegoutdino", "author_bot": false, "content": "能夠養出5隊50-60級的玩家大概也不太需要這些資訊XD\n也不是說專注在325這點上，\n但現在就已經有人閱讀感受不好了\n所以才建議要算上限就用350，要給新手的攻略就用300或不計\n或是額外提醒這獎勵新手難以達成，在計算時需憑自身能力衡量", "timestamp": "2024-04-26T03:27:07.978000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-04-26T03:28:38.376000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1231906620980596757", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "七萬銀芯囤囤鼠教你如何以性價比最高的方式實現資源管理！", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1227516925479747584", "1174179680056791130", "1174180524034637854"]}
