{"id": "1233261500546682950", "channel_id": "1231906620980596757", "type": 0, "author_id": "392840163732226058", "author_name": "vegoutdino", "author_bot": false, "content": "其他還有珍稀素材的介紹，目前連續兩次活動（神父、24）都出現調查徽章的無限取得方式，有限制獲取量的資源又少了一種", "timestamp": "2024-04-26T03:40:54.621000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1231906620980596757", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "七萬銀芯囤囤鼠教你如何以性價比最高的方式實現資源管理！", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1227516925479747584", "1174179680056791130", "1174180524034637854"]}
